  silent s/Ð/\&ETH;/eg
  silent s/Ñ/\&Ntilde;/eg
  silent s/Ò/\&Ograve;/eg
  silent s/Ó/\&Oacute;/eg
  silent s/Ô/\&Ocirc;/eg
  silent s/Õ/\&Otilde;/eg
  silent s/Ö/\&Ouml;/eg
